Services

DevicePreauthorization

http://linksys.com/jnap/devicepreauthorization/DevicePreauthorization
This service provides actions and settings for device preauthorization and onboarding of preauthorized devices.

Service Actions

  • AddPreauthorizedDevices
  • GetOnboardWiFiPreauthorizedStatus
  • GetPreauthorizedDevices
  • OnboardWiFiPreauthorizedDevices

Actions

AddPreauthorizedDevices

http://linksys.com/jnap/devicepreauthorization/AddPreauthorizedDevices
This action preauthorizes devices for onboarding to the network.

Note:

This action is safe to call within the context of a transaction.

Input Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
deviceIDs string[] no A list of ID's of the devices to be preauthorized. A device ID cannot be an empty string.

Output Parameters

This action does not have any output parameters.

Result

http://linksys.com/jnap/devicepreauthorization/AddPreauthorizedDevicesResult
Value Description
OK Success.
Error
ErrorDeviceNotInMasterMode The action only works in Master mode.
ErrorInvalidDeviceID One or more of the values in deviceIDs is invalid.
_ErrorAbortedAction
_ErrorInvalidInput
_ErrorInvalidOutput
_ErrorNotReady
_ErrorSessionVerification
_ErrorUnauthorized
_ErrorUnexpected
_ErrorUnknownAction
_ErrorUnknownSession

Sample Transaction

POST [request-uri] HTTP/1.1
Host: 192.168.1.1
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in request body]
X-JNAP-Action: "http://linksys.com/jnap/devicepreauthorization/AddPreauthorizedDevices"

{
  "deviceIDs": [
    "example string"
  ]
}
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in response body]

{
  "result": "OK"
}

GetOnboardWiFiPreauthorizedStatus

http://linksys.com/jnap/devicepreauthorization/GetOnboardWiFiPreauthorizedStatus
This action gets the status of the WiFi preauthorized onboarding process initiated by OnboardWiFiPreauthorizedDevices.

Note:

This action is safe to call within the context of a transaction.

Input Parameters

This action does not have any input parameters.

Output Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
lastTriggered DateTime yes The time when the WiFi preauthorized onboarding process was last triggered. This parameter will exist only if the preauthorized onboarding process has previously been triggered.
isRunning bool no Whether the WiFi preauthorized onboarding process is running.
status OnboardWiFiPreauthStatus yes The status of the WiFi preauthorized onboarding process. This parameter will exist only if the process has been previously triggered and isRunning is false
errorInfo OnboardingErrorInfo yes Information about errors that occurred during the process. This parameter will be present only if status is Error

Result

http://linksys.com/jnap/devicepreauthorization/GetOnboardWiFiPreauthorizedStatusResult
Value Description
OK Success.
Error
ErrorDeviceNotInMasterMode The action only works in Master mode.
_ErrorAbortedAction
_ErrorInvalidInput
_ErrorInvalidOutput
_ErrorNotReady
_ErrorSessionVerification
_ErrorUnauthorized
_ErrorUnexpected
_ErrorUnknownAction
_ErrorUnknownSession

Sample Transaction

POST [request-uri] HTTP/1.1
Host: 192.168.1.1
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in request body]
X-JNAP-Action: "http://linksys.com/jnap/devicepreauthorization/GetOnboardWiFiPreauthorizedStatus"

{
}
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in response body]

{
  "result": "OK",
  "output": {
    "lastTriggered": "2017-03-15T00:00:00Z",
    "isRunning": false,
    "status": "Success",
    "errorInfo": {
      "errorDescription": "Failed discovering devices",
      "deviceErrors": [
        {
          "deviceID": "S123456789",
          "errorDescription": "CannotGetIPAddressError"
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}

GetPreauthorizedDevices

http://linksys.com/jnap/devicepreauthorization/GetPreauthorizedDevices
This action gets a list of devices that have been preauthorized for onboarding to the network.

Note:

This action is safe to call within the context of a transaction.

Input Parameters

This action does not have any input parameters.

Output Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
deviceIDs string[] no A list preauthorized device ID's. This list will be empty if no devices have been preauthorized.

Result

http://linksys.com/jnap/devicepreauthorization/GetPreauthorizedDevicesResult
Value Description
OK Success.
Error
_ErrorAbortedAction
_ErrorInvalidInput
_ErrorInvalidOutput
_ErrorNotReady
_ErrorSessionVerification
_ErrorUnauthorized
_ErrorUnexpected
_ErrorUnknownAction
_ErrorUnknownSession

}

OnboardWiFiPreauthorizedDevices

http://linksys.com/jnap/devicepreauthorization/OnboardWiFiPreauthorizedDevices
This action initiates the process of onboarding WiFi preauthorized devices to the network. After this action is called, GetOnboardWiFiPreauthorizedStatus can be called to monitor the status of the process.

Input Parameters

This action does not have any input parameters.

Output Parameters

This action does not have any output parameters.

Result

http://linksys.com/jnap/devicepreauthorization/OnboardWiFiPreauthorizedDevicesResult
Value Description
OK Success.
Error
ErrorDeviceNotInMasterMode The action only works in Master mode.
ErrorNoPreauthorizedDevices There are no preauthorized devices to onboard.
ErrorOnboardWiFiPreauthorizedAlreadyRunning The WiFi preauthorized onborading process is already running.
_ErrorAbortedAction
_ErrorDisallowedAction
_ErrorInvalidInput
_ErrorInvalidOutput
_ErrorNotReady
_ErrorSessionVerification
_ErrorUnauthorized
_ErrorUnexpected
_ErrorUnknownAction
_ErrorUnknownSession

Sample Transaction

POST [request-uri] HTTP/1.1
Host: 192.168.1.1
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in request body]
X-JNAP-Action: "http://linksys.com/jnap/devicepreauthorization/OnboardWiFiPreauthorizedDevices"

{
}
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in response body]

{
  "result": "OK"
}

Structures

DeviceErrorInfo

http://linksys.com/jnap/devicepreauthorization/DeviceErrorInfo
Data structure containing information about an error that occurred while onboarding a specific device.

Structure Members

Member Name Type Optional Description
deviceID string no The unique device identifier.
errorDescription string no A description of the error.

OnboardingErrorInfo

http://linksys.com/jnap/devicepreauthorization/OnboardingErrorInfo
Data structure containing information about errors that occurred during the onboarding process.

Structure Members

Member Name Type Optional Description
errorDescription string no A general description of the error that occurred.
deviceErrors DeviceErrorInfo[] no A list of device-specific onboarding errors. This list will be empty if no device onboarding errors occurred.

Enumerations

OnboardWiFiPreauthStatus

http://linksys.com/jnap/devicepreauthorization/OnboardWiFiPreauthStatus
This service provides actions and settings for device preauthorization and onboarding of preauthorized devices. Possible states of a WiFi preauthorized onboarding process.

Enumeration Values

Value Description
Success Successfully onboarded preauthorized devices.
Error An error occurred during the preauthorized onboarding process.
